{{medical}}

{{Infobox medical condition (new)
| name = 性功能障碍
| field = [[精神科|精神科]]、[[泌尿科|泌尿科]]、[[婦產科|婦產科]]
| synonyms =性功能紊亂、性障碍
}}
'''性功能障碍'''（{{lang-en|Sexual dysfunction、sexual malfunction或sexual disorder}}，或稱'''性功能紊亂'''、'''性障碍'''），是指任何在[[陳馳性反应周期|陳馳性反应周期]]中，導致人們產生心理痛苦的問題<ref name="人类的性存在">{{Cite book|author1=珍妮特·S·海德|author2=約翰·D·德拉馬特|title=人类的性存在|url=https://archive.org/details/renleidexingcunz0008hyde|publisher=上海社會科学院出版社|year=2005|isbn=7-80681-730-1}}</ref>{{rp|538}}。該些性反應包括[[性興奮|性興奮]]、[[性慾|性慾望]]、[[性偏好|性偏好]]或[[性高潮|性高潮]]。根據DSM-5，當事人需至少在六個月內感到極度痛苦或影響[[人際關係|人際關係]]，才可診斷作任何形式的性功能障碍（不包括由物質或藥物引起的性功能障礙）<ref>{{cite book|last=Nolen-Hoeksema|first=Susan|title=Abnormal Psychology|url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781308211503|year=2014|publisher=McGraw-Hill|location=2 Penn Plaza, New York, NY 10121|isbn=978-1-259-06072-4|pages=[https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781308211503/page/366 366]–367}}</ref>。性功能障礙會對患者的性生活質量產生重大影響<ref name= "eden">{{cite journal | author = Eden K.J., Wylie K.R. | year = 2009 | title = Quality of sexual life and menopause | url = | journal = Women's Health | volume = 5 | issue = 4| pages = 385–396 | doi = 10.2217/whe.09.24 | pmid = 19586430 }}</ref>。

對性功能障碍的治療而言，獲取和評估患者的性史、一般健康情況及其他性問題（如有）是十分重要的。評估患者的臨場[[焦慮|焦慮感]]、[[內疚|內疚感]]、[[憂慮|憂慮感]]及[[壓力_(醫學)|心理壓力]]為性功能障碍管理最佳化的一部分。許多性功能障碍是依據由[[麥斯特與強生|麥斯特與強生]]所提出的[[人类性反应周期|人类性反应周期]]來進行定義。該套週期隨後經性治療師{{link-en|海倫·辛格·卡普蘭|Helen Singer Kaplan}}之手進行修改<ref>{{cite book|last1=Johnson|first1=William H. Masters [and] Virginia E.|title=Human sexual inadequacy|date=1970|publisher=Churchill|location=London|isbn=978-0700001934|edition=2. print}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Kaplan|first1=Helen Singer|title=The new sex therapy; active treatment of sexual dysfunctions.|url=https://archive.org/details/newsextherapyact00kapl|date=1974|publisher=Brunner/Mazel|location=New York|isbn=978-0876300831}}</ref>。

==分类==
性功能障礙可分為四大類：[[性慾障礙|性慾障礙]]、[[性喚起障礙|喚起障礙]]、[[性高潮障礙|性高潮障礙]]以及[[性交疼痛|性疼痛障碍]]。
===性慾障礙===
{{Main|性慾低下症}}
性慾障礙（或性慾過低症）的特徵在於患者在一段時間內，缺乏或完全沒有進行[[性慾|性行為的慾望]]或出現[[性幻想|性幻想]]<ref name="Merck Low Sexual Desire Disorder">{{cite book|year=2011|chapter=Low Sexual Desire Disorder|chapterurl=https://www.msdmanuals.com/home/women-s-health-issues/sexual-dysfunction-in-women/low-sexual-desire-disorder|editor1-last=Basson|editor1-first=Rosemary|title=The Merck Manual of Diagnosis & Therapy|edition=19th|location=Whitehouse Station, NJ|publisher=Merck Sharp & Dohme Corp., A Subsidiary of Merck & Co., Inc.|isbn=978-0-911910-19-3|access-date=2018-12-26|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093341/https://www.msdmanuals.com/home/women-s-health-issues/sexual-dysfunction-in-women/low-sexual-desire-disorder|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這一障礙的定義廣至一般性地缺乏性慾，窄至對現在的性伴侶缺乏性慾。患上性慾低落障礙的人在這之前可能性功能正常，也可能經常保持在低性慾狀態。

它的成因因人而異。可能的病因包括女性[[雌激素|雌激素]]水平下降、兩性皆會出現的[[睾酮|睾酮]]水平下降、年老、懷孕、疲倦、藥物（比如[[选择性5-羟色胺再摄取抑制剂|选择性5-羟色胺再摄取抑制剂]]（SSRIs））、像[[焦慮症|焦慮症]]和[[抑鬱症|抑鬱症]]般的精神疾病。雖然性慾低落的原因有許多，但當中只有一部為實證研究的目標<ref>Maurice, William (2007): "Sexual Desire Disorders in Men." in ed. Leiblum, Sandra:  ''Principles and Practice of Sex Therapy'' (4th ed.)  The Guilford Press.  New York</ref>。

===性喚起障礙===
{{Main|性喚起障礙}}
性喚起障礙在以前一般稱為性冷感（frigidity，專用於女性）及[[性無能|性無能]]（impotence，專用於男性），現今就改用相對較不帶有主觀判斷的用詞。性無能改稱[[勃起功能障碍|勃起功能障碍]]；性冷感則分拆為若干可分作四大類別的特定障礙：缺乏性慾、缺乏性喚起、缺乏性高潮，以及在性行為過程中感到疼痛<ref>{{cite journal | author = Hartley H | year = 2006 | title = The 'pinking' of Viagra culture: Drug industry efforts to create and repackage sex drugs for women | doi = 10.1177/1363460706065058 | journal = Sexualities | volume = 9 | issue = 3| page = 365 }}</ref>。它一般是指對性刺激缺乏生理或心理反應<ref name="Merck Sexual Arousal Disorders">{{cite book|year=2011|chapter=Sexual Arousal Disorders|chapterurl=https://www.msdmanuals.com/home/women-s-health-issues/sexual-dysfunction-in-women/sexual-arousal-disorders|editor1-last=Basson|editor1-first=Rosemary|title=The Merck Manual of Diagnosis & Therapy|edition=19th|location=Whitehouse Station, NJ|publisher=Merck Sharp & Dohme Corp., A Subsidiary of Merck & Co., Inc.|isbn=978-0-911910-19-3|access-date=2018-12-26|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812193948/https://www.msdmanuals.com/home/women-s-health-issues/sexual-dysfunction-in-women/sexual-arousal-disorders|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

患上這一種障礙的男女皆可能會將其具體表現作避免及不想跟伴侶發生性接觸。男性的具體表現可為陰莖在性行為期間無法勃起或維持勃起、在性行為期間缺乏性快樂及性興奮。

這一障礙可因生理因素而起，比如血流下降或陰道分泌液缺乏<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|542}}<ref name="Merck Sexual Arousal Disorders"/>。慢性疾病及跟伴侶的關係也是其原因<ref name="Merck Sexual Arousal Disorders"/>。

===勃起功能障碍===
{{main|勃起功能障碍}}
勃起功能障碍是指陰莖在性行為期間無法勃起或維持勃起<ref>{{cite web|title=Erectile Dysfunction|url=https://medlineplus.gov/erectiledysfunction.html|accessdate=2018-12-26|publisher=MedlinePlus|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222234356/https://medlineplus.gov/erectiledysfunction.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|538-39}}。它的成因各式各樣，其中包括神经系统病变、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]，以及[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Neurogenic Sexual Dysfunction in Men and Women |publisher=Neurologic Bladder, Bowel and Sexual Dysfunction |url=https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/e6da/d23c945e95e02c99079be4ec33c661d51fab.pdf |accessdate=2015-08-10 |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618002606/https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/e6da/d23c945e95e02c99079be4ec33c661d51fab.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="趙建剛 2010"/>；心血管疾病會使流入陰莖組織的血流減少<ref name="趙建剛 2010">{{cite journal|author=趙建剛|title=老年人勃起功能障礙相關因素之探討|url=http://www.wacshome.net/china/CESLR-No_1.pdf|journal=華人老人性生活研究|issue=1|date=2010-01-05|access-date=2018-10-03|pages=34-43|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222234350/http://www.wacshome.net/china/CESLR-No_1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

勃起功能障碍的成因包括心生理兩方面<ref name=health.am>{{cite web | author=Tom F. Lue, MD | title=Causes of Erectile Dysfunction | publisher=Armenian Health Network, Health.am | work=Erectile dysfunction | url=http://www.health.am/sex/more/causes_of_erectile_dysfunction/ | year=2006 | accessdate=2007-10-07 | archive-date=2021-02-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222234416/http://www.health.am/sex/more/causes_of_erectile_dysfunction/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="趙建剛 2010"/>。心因性的勃起功能障碍可透過患者認為能有幫助的事物或行為來解決——安慰劑治療對此有着強烈的效果。相比之下，物理損傷會顯得較為嚴重。勃起功能障碍的成因之一為嚴重的骨盆神經受損，該些神經從骶丛延伸至前列腺旁邊，結腸和前列腺手術皆可使其受損<ref>{{cite book|title=Male Sexual Dysfunction: A Clinical Guide|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=iuoCDgAAQBAJ&pg=PA203&lpg=PA203|access-date=2018-12-26|pages=203-204|editor1-last=Minhas|editor1-first=Suks|editor2-last=Mulhall|date=2016-12-16|editor2-first=John|isbn=9781118746554|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520104738/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=iuoCDgAAQBAJ&pg=PA203&lpg=PA203|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

糖尿病也是勃起功能障碍的普遍成因之一，對於男性而言更是如此。勃起功能障礙的原因還包括心血管疾病、多發性硬化症、腎衰竭和脊髓損傷等疾病<ref>Nolen-Hoeksema, S. (2013). Sexual Dysfnctions. In Abnormal Psychology. McGraw Hill Education.</ref>。

據估計，約3000萬名美國男性患有勃起功能障礙，以全球計則有1.52億名男性患上之<ref>{{cite journal | author = NIH. Consensus Development Panel on Impotence.| year = 1993 | title = Impotence | url = | journal = Journal of the American Medical Association | volume = 270 | issue = | pages = 83–90 | doi=10.1001/jama.270.1.83}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Ayta I, Mckinlay J, Krane R | year = 1999 | title = The likely worldwide increase in erectile dysfunction between 1995 and 2025 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_bju-international_1999-07_84_1/page/50| journal = BJU Int | volume = 84 | issue = 1| pages = 50–56 | doi=10.1046/j.1464-410x.1999.00142.x}}</ref>。然而相關報告數字仍因醫學知識水平低下、社會污名等因素而低於實際水平，使得研究者難以準確估計。

拉丁語「impotentia coeundi」的意思是指陰莖喪失跟陰道接合的能力；現今則較多以更精確的用語代指這種情況，比如「erectile dysfunction」。

===早發性射精===
{{main|早發性射精}}
早發性射精指的是當事人在伴侶達至[[性高潮|性高潮]]之前射精，或在滿意的性行為持續時間前射精。儘管性交的持續時間並沒有正確標準，但一般而言研究者會判斷從接合開始計少於2分鐘即為早發性射精<ref>Waldinger M.D., Berenden H.H., Blok B.F., et al. ''Premature Ejaculation and Serotengeric Anti-depressants - Induced Delayed Ejaculation: The Involvement of the Serotonergic System.'' Behavioural Brain Res. 1998;92(2): 111-118</ref>。要診斷當事人患有早發性射精，其必須符合「具有早發性射精的慢性病史」、「控制射精能力欠佳」和「該問題引起自身或伴侶的不滿」這些條件<ref name=Diaz>Diaz V.A. & Close J.D. ''Male Sexual Dysfunction'' Primary Care 2010;37(3): 473 - 489.'</ref>。

以往早發性射精一般視作是心理因素所導致的，但新的理論指出其可歸因於神經生物因素<ref>Lauman E.O., Nicolosi, A., Glasser D.B., et al. ''Sexual Problems among women and men aged 40 to 80 years: Prevalence and Correlates Identified in a GLobal Study of Sexual Attitudes and Behaviours.'' International Journal of Impotence Research. 2005;7(1): 39 - 57.</ref>。

===性高潮障礙===
{{Main|性高潮障礙}}
性高潮障礙是指當事人在經歷包含最少75%時段性接觸的正常性興奮期後，仍不能或難以達至高潮的情況<ref>{{cite book|last1=Nolen-Hoeksema|first1=Susan|title=Abnormal Psychology|url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781308211503|date=2014|publisher=McGraw-Hill|location=New York, NY|isbn=978-1-259-06072-4|page=[https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781308211503/page/368 368]}}</ref>。這一障礙可由生理、心理或藥物因素所導致<ref name=Berman>''For Women Only, Revised Edition: A Revolutionary Guide to Reclaiming Your Sex Life'' by Berman, J. Bumiller, E. and Berman L. (2005), Owl Books, NY. {{ISBN|978-0-8050-7883-1}}</ref><ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|545}}。SSRI型抗抑鬱藥是一類常會引起性高潮障礙的藥物，因為它們能使高潮延遲，甚至使其完全消失<ref>{{Cite journal |vauthors=Hu XH, Bull SA, Hunkeler EM |title=Incidence and duration of side effects and those rated as bothersome with selective serotonin reuptake inhibitor treatment for depression: patient report versus physician estimate |journal=The Journal of Clinical Psychiatry |volume=65 |issue=7 |pages=959–65 |date=July 2004 |pmid=15291685 |url=http://article.psychiatrist.com/?ContentType=START&ID=10000968 |doi=10.4088/JCP.v65n0712 |display-authors=etal |access-date=2018-12-31 |archive-date=2012-07-01 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120701173532/http://article.psychiatrist.com/?ContentType=START&ID=10000968 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|vauthors=Landén M, Högberg P, Thase ME |title=Incidence of sexual side effects in refractory depression during treatment with citalopram or paroxetine |journal=The Journal of Clinical Psychiatry |volume=66 |issue=1 |pages=100–06 |date=January 2005 |pmid=15669895 |doi=10.4088/JCP.v66n0114}}</ref>。[[更年期|更年期]]也是性高潮障礙的成因之一，約33%經歷過更年期的女性報稱在達至高潮這一問題上出現困難<ref>Nolen-Hoeksema, Susan. "Abnormal Psychology". McGraw-Hill Humanities/Social Sciences/Languages; 6 Edition, 2013. p.368.</ref>。

===性疼痛障碍===
性疼痛障碍，亦稱[[性交疼痛|性交疼痛]]，是指性交過程中所出現的疼痛<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|542}}。這一障碍以女性患者佔大多數。[[陰道痙攣|陰道痙攣]]是指因為骨盆底肌肉無意識地繃緊，而令女方在性交或往陰道插入任何物件時感到痛苦<ref name=Fer2016>{{cite book |last1=Ferri |first1=Fred F. |title=Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2017 E-Book: 5 Books in 1 |date=2016 |publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences |isbn=9780323448383 |page=1330 |url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA1330 |language=en |access-date=2018-12-31 |archive-date=2019-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520043127/https://books.google.ca/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA1330 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Ferri">{{cite book|author=Fred F. Ferri|title=Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2013,5 Books in 1, Expert Consult — Online and Print,1: Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2013|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=0323083730|year=2012|page=1134|accessdate=2014-11-29|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OR3VERnvzzEC&pg=PA1134|archive-date=2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326122056/http://books.google.com/books?id=OR3VERnvzzEC&pg=PA1134|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這跟性交疼痛有密切關係<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|542}}。

性交疼痛可能是由女性陰道潤滑液缺乏所致<ref name="Dyspareunia Britannica">{{cite web|title=Dyspareunia|url=https://www.britannica.com/science/dyspareunia|work=Encyclopaedia Britannica|accessdate=2019-01-03|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026203303/https://www.britannica.com/science/dyspareunia|dead-url=no}}</ref>，更年期<ref name=Hoffman2012>{{cite book | last = Hoffman | first = Barbara | title = Williams gynecology | publisher = McGraw-Hill Medical | location = New York | year = 2012 | isbn = 9780071716727|pages=555–56 }}</ref>及哺乳期<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Bachmann GA, Leiblum SR, Kemmann E, Colburn DW, Swartzman L, Shelden R |title=Sexual expression and its determinants in the post-menopausal woman |journal=Maturitas |volume=6 |issue=1 |pages=19–29 |date=July 1984  |pmid=6433154 |doi=10.1016/0378-5122(84)90062-8}}</ref>期間的激素變化會導致陰道潤滑液分泌減少，此外性興奮不足也會導致之<ref>{{cite book|title=Psychoanalytic Psychotherapy: A Handbook|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=BT9ZDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT389|publisher=Karnac Books|last1=Elzer|first1=Matthias|last2=Gerlach|first2=Alf|date=2014-03-17|isbn=9781781812105|access-date=2019-01-03|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521153727/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=BT9ZDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT389|dead-url=no}}</ref>。殺精藥膏過敏<ref name="人类的性存在"/>{{rp|546}}及對性存有恐懼<ref name="Dyspareunia Britannica"/>也是其可能成因。

陰道痙攣的根本成因為對性交疼痛存有恐懼<ref name=Mer2013>{{cite web |title=Vaginismus |url=https://www.merckmanuals.com/professional/gynecology-and-obstetrics/sexual-dysfunction-in-women/vaginismus |website=Merck Manuals Professional Edition |accessdate=2018-10-15 |year=2013 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118064127/https://www.merckmanuals.com/professional/gynecology-and-obstetrics/sexual-dysfunction-in-women/vaginismus |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，其風險因子包括[[性侵犯|性侵犯]]史、曾患有子宮內膜異位症及[[陰道炎|陰道炎]]<ref name=Fer2016/>。[[外阴疼痛|外阴疼痛]]及外陰前庭炎為另外兩類的性疼痛障碍，主要影響婦科外陰部位，其原因未明<ref>{{cite journal |author=Feldhaus-Dahir |title=The Causes and Prevalence of Vestibulodynia: A Vulvar Pain Disorder |journal=Urologic Nursing |volume=31 |date=January–February 2011 |pages=51–54 |pmid= 21542444 |issue=1}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pmid=21542444 |year=2011 |author1=Feldhaus-Dahir |first1=M |title=The causes and prevalence of vestibulodynia: A vulvar pain disorder |journal=Urologic nursing |volume=31 |issue=1 |pages=51–4 }}</ref><ref name=pmid1659198>{{cite journal |vauthors=Marinoff SC, Turner ML |title=Vulvar vestibulitis syndrome: an overview |journal=Am J Obstet Gynecol |volume=165 |issue=4 Pt 2 |pages=1228–33 |year=1991 |pmid=1659198 |doi=}}</ref><ref name=Peckham86>{{cite journal |vauthors=Peckham BM, Maki DG, Patterson JJ, Hafez GR |title=Focal vulvitis: a characteristic syndrome and cause of dyspareunia. Features, natural history, and management |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-obstetrics-and-gynecology_1986-04_154_4/page/855 |journal=Am J Obstet Gynecol |volume=154 |issue=4 |pages=855–64 |date= 1986 |pmid=3963075 }}</ref>。
===性高潮後障碍===
性高潮後障碍會使人於高潮或[[射精|射精]]過後產生症狀。[[性交後憂鬱|性交後憂鬱]]指的是性交後感到憂鬱或焦慮，可於性交後5分鐘-2小時發生<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/20/health/20iht-20mind.19507430.html |title=Sex and depression: In the brain, if not the mind |newspaper=New York Times |date=2009-01-20 |accessdate=2011-10-05 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041518/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/20/health/20iht-20mind.19507430.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部分人在性活動期間感到頭骨和頸部存有痛楚，這稱為性頭痛<ref name="cutrer2014">{{cite journal | author = Cutrer, F. M. | author2 = DeLange, J. | last-author-amp = yes | year = 2014 | title = Cough, exercise, and sex headaches. | journal = Neurologic Clinics | volume = 32 | issue = 2 | pages = 433–450 | doi = 10.1016/j.ncl.2013.11.012 | pmid=24703538}}</ref>。

一小部分男性患有[[性高潮後病情症候群|性高潮後病情症候群]]（POIS），患者在射精後可能會感到全身肌肉嚴重疼痛，以及其他相关的症狀，症狀可持續長達一周<ref name=Balon2005>{{cite book | title=Handbook of Sexual Dysfunction | url=https://archive.org/details/handbookofsexual0000unse_d3f6 | publisher=Taylor & Francis |veditors=Balon R, Segraves RT | year=2005 | isbn=978-0-8247-5826-4}}</ref><ref name=Wylie2015>{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oH64CAAAQBAJ&lpg=PA75&dq=Post%20orgaasmic%20illness%20syndrome&pg=PA75#v=onepage&q=Post-orgasmic%20illness%20syndrome&f=false | title=ABC of Sexual Health | publisher=John Wiley & Sons | year=2015 | page=75 | isbn=978-1-118-66556-5 | editor=Wylie KR | accessdate=2015-10-21 | archive-date=2020-11-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105024937/https://books.google.com/books?id=oH64CAAAQBAJ&lpg=PA75&dq=Post%20orgaasmic%20illness%20syndrome&pg=PA75#v=onepage&q=Post-orgasmic%20illness%20syndrome&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=GARD>{{cite encyclopedia|title=Postorgasmic illness syndrome |encyclopedia=Genetic and Rare Diseases Information Center (GARD) |publisher=National Institutes of Health |accessdate=2015-07-30 |year=2015 |url=https://rarediseases.info.nih.gov/gard/10809/postorgasmic-illness-syndrome/resources/1 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305193016/https://rarediseases.info.nih.gov/gard/10809/postorgasmic-illness-syndrome/resources/1 |archivedate=2016-03-05 }}</ref>。一些醫生推測性高潮後病情症候群在人民中出現的机率可能比已經在學術文獻中報告的更大<ref name=Ashby2010>{{cite journal|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1743-6109.2010.01707.x/abstract;jsessionid=EC000313CA779834B8938F5F698E5FD3.f03t04 |title=Postorgasm illness syndrome--a spectrum of illnesses. |vauthors=Ashby J, Goldmeier D |journal=J Sex Med. |date=2010-05 |volume=7 |issue=5 |pages=1976–81 |doi=10.1111/j.1743-6109.2010.01707 |pmid=20214722 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221024829/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1743-6109.2010.01707.x/abstract%3Bjsessionid%3DEC000313CA779834B8938F5F698E5FD3.f03t04 |archivedate=2016-12-21 }}</ref>，而且許多性高潮後病情症候群患者尚未確診<ref name=McMahon2014>{{cite journal|url=https://www.statusplus.net/issm/saopaulo2014/presentations/082.pdf |title=Post-Orgasmic Illness Syndrome |author=McMahon CG |journal=16th World Meeting on Sexual Medicine |date=2014-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110554/https://www.statusplus.net/issm/saopaulo2014/presentations/082.pdf |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。其症狀包括呼吸急促、感覺異常、心悸、頭痛、失語、噁心、眼睛發癢、發燒、肌肉疼痛、虛弱和疲勞<ref name=Waldinger2016>{{cite encyclopedia | title=Post-Orgasmic Illness Syndrome | encyclopedia=Handbook of Clinical Sexuality for Mental Health Professionals | publisher=Routledge | author=Waldinger MD |veditors=Levine S, Risen CB, Althof SE | year=2016 | edition=3rd | pages=380 | url= | isbn=9781317507451}}</ref><ref name=Waldinger2002>{{cite journal | url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/009262302760328280 | title=Postorgasmic illness syndrome: two cases. | vauthors=Waldinger MD, Schweitzer DH | journal=J Sex Marital Ther. | date=May 2002 | volume=28 | issue=3 | pages=251–5 | doi=10.1080/009262302760328280 | pmid=11995603 | access-date=2019-01-03 | archive-date=2021-12-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211221150107/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/009262302760328280 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Wylie2015/><ref name=Jiang2015>{{cite journal | url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/jsm.12813/abstract;jsessionid=AECC19DFFF09F5D332636C165FA580AA.f03t02 | title=Postorgasmic illness syndrome (POIS) in a Chinese man: no proof for IgE-mediated allergy to semen. | vauthors=Jiang N, Xi G, Li H, Yin J | journal=J. Sex. Med. | date=Mar 2015 | volume=12 | issue=3 | pages=840–5 | doi=10.1111/jsm.12813 | pmid=25630453 | access-date=2019-01-03 | archive-date=2017-08-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829121913/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/jsm.12813/abstract;jsessionid=AECC19DFFF09F5D332636C165FA580AA.f03t02 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Nguyen2018>{{cite journal |title=Post-Orgasmic Illness Syndrome: A Review |vauthors=Nguyen HM, Bala A, Gabrielson AT, Hellstrom WJ |journal=Sexual Medicine Reviews |date=January 6, 2018 |volume=6 |issue=1 |pages=11–15 |doi=10.1016/j.sxmr.2017.08.006 |pmid=29128269}}</ref>。這種病症的病因尚不清楚，但它被認為跟免疫系統或自主神經系統有關。美國國立衛生研究院定義它為罕見疾病；它沒有已知的治癒方法或治療方法<ref name="rarediseases.info.nih.gov">{{Cite web | url=https://rarediseases.info.nih.gov/diseases/10809/postorgasmic-illness-syndrome | title=Postorgasmic illness syndrome | Genetic and Rare Diseases Information Center (GARD) – an NCATS Program | access-date=2019-01-03 | archive-date=2019-06-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616035117/https://rarediseases.info.nih.gov/diseases/10809/postorgasmic-illness-syndrome | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===盆底功能障礙===
{{Main|{{link-en|盆底功能障礙|Pelvic floor dysfunction}}}}
盆底功能障礙是男女性功能障礙的根本原因之一，其可通過物理治療恢復<ref name="malepelvicfloor.com">{{Cite web | url=http://malepelvicfloor.com/sd.html | title=Male Pelvic Floor: Advanced Massage and Bodywork | access-date=2018-12-31 | archive-date=2019-05-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502090409/http://www.malepelvicfloor.com/sd.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite journal | author = | year = 2008 | title = The Role of Pelvic Floor Physical Therapy in the Treatment of Pelvic and Genital Pain-Related Sexual Dysfunction | url = | journal = Journal of Sexual Medicine | volume = 5 | issue = | pages = 513–523 }}</ref>。

===罕有男性性功能障碍===
激素缺乏為勃起功能障礙的罕見成因。患有像克氏综合征般會使人睾丸發育不全的疾病、接受過放射治療、化療，及童年患有腮腺炎的人的睾丸皆可能會受損，不能產生睾酮。其他激素誘導勃起功能障礙的成因包括腦腫瘤、甲狀腺功能亢進、甲狀腺功能減退，及腎上腺疾病<ref>[http://www.askmen.com/dating/love_tip_300/381_love_tip.html Strange sexual disorders] {{Wayback|url=http://www.askmen.com/dating/love_tip_300/381_love_tip.html |date=20210117070907 }} Ask Men. Retrieved on February 18, 2010</ref>。

藥物也是勃起功能障礙的成因。 服用降血壓藥或使用抗精神病藥、抗抑鬱藥、鎮靜劑、麻醉藥、抗酸劑或酒精的人可能會出現性功能和性慾減退問題<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gupta |first1=A |last2=Chaudhry |first2=M |last3=Elewski |first3=B |title=Tinea corporis, tinea cruris, tinea nigra, and piedra |journal=Dermatologic Clinics |volume=21 |pages=395–400, v |year=2003 |doi=10.1016/S0733-8635(03)00031-7 |pmid=12956194 |issue=3}}</ref>。

[[陰莖異常勃起|陰莖異常勃起]]是指陰莖即使在没受到任何刺激的情况下，也在数小时或以上的跨度内维持勃起。當血液困在陰莖內無法流出時便會發生這種情況。如果不及時治療，便有機會導致永久性的勃起能力喪失疤痕。患有鐮刀型紅血球疾病和濫用某些藥物的人較易出現這種情況<ref>[http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/777603-overview Priapism in Emergency Medicine] {{Wayback|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/777603-overview |date=20130930200155 }}, [[eMedicine|eMedicine]]. Retrieved on 2010-02-18</ref>。

